title: The Ferret 01-10 (1992-1994|Malibu|Bsg) [FIXED]
description:
The Ferret 01-10 from Malibu Comics, the complete run. The Ferret is an agile warrior and member of the Protectors. Requested by Justin_Cook. Scans by Bsg; thanks to them for their work, please seed and enjoy! :-)	

*NOTE - I had previously uploaded this series but there was a problem with issues 5, 6, and 7 not opening correctly. I have re-downoladed them and tested on my CDisplayEX, they should be fine now. If not, however, please let me know. Thanks!
